result.detailedDescription.articleBody: Mandalorians are fictional people associated with the planet Mandalore in the Star Wars universe and franchise created by George Lucas.
result.name: Mandalorians

result.detailedDescription.articleBody: The third season of the American television series The Mandalorian stars Pedro Pascal as the title character, a bounty hunter traveling to Mandalore to redeem his past transgressions with his companion Grogu.
result.name: The Mandalorian

result.detailedDescription.articleBody: The Mandalorian is an American space western television series created by Jon Favreau for the streaming service Disney+. It is the first live-action series in the Star Wars franchise, beginning five years after the events of Return of the Jedi, and stars Pedro Pascal as the title character, a lone bounty hunter who goes on the run to protect "the Child".
result.name: The Mandalorian

result.detailedDescription.articleBody: The Mandalorian, or Mando for short, is a fictional character in the Star Wars franchise, who appears as the titular protagonist of the Disney+ television series The Mandalorian and also appears in its spin-off The Book of Boba Fett.
result.name: The Mandalorian
